{% extends 'base.html' %}
{% load static %}

{% block body %}

<!-- ========== NAVBAR ========== -->
<nav class="navbar" id="navbar">
  <div class="container">
    <a href="/" class="nav-brand">
      <div class="logo-icon">E</div>
      <span>ENABLE PROGRAM</span>
    </a>
    <ul class="nav-links" id="navLinks">
      <li><a href="/">Home</a></li>
      <li class="nav-dropdown">
        <a href="#" class="active">About <i class="fas fa-chevron-down" style="font-size:.625rem;margin-left:4px"></i></a>
        <div class="dropdown-menu">
          <a href="/about/"><i class="fas fa-building"></i> About ENF</a>
          <a href="/founder/" class="active"><i class="fas fa-user-tie"></i> Founder &amp; Trustees</a>
          <a href="/management/"><i class="fas fa-users-cog"></i> Management Team</a>
        </div>
      </li>
      <li><a href="/programs/">Programs</a></li>
      <li><a href="/partners/">Partners</a></li>
      <li><a href="/scholarships/">Scholarships</a></li>
      <li><a href="/news/">News</a></li>
      <li><a href="#contact">Contact</a></li>
    </ul>
    <div class="nav-actions">
      <a href="javascript:void(0)" class="btn btn-primary btn-sm" onclick="openLoginModal()"><i class="fas fa-sign-in-alt"></i> Login</a>
    </div>
    <button class="mobile-menu-btn" onclick="toggleMobileMenu()"><i class="fas fa-bars"></i></button>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- ========== LOGIN MODAL ========== -->
<div class="login-modal-overlay" id="loginModal">
  <div class="login-modal" style="position:relative">
    <button class="login-modal-close" onclick="closeLoginModal()"><i class="fas fa-times"></i></button>
    <div class="login-modal-header">
      <h2>Welcome Back</h2>
      <p>Select your role to continue</p>
    </div>
    <div class="login-role-grid">
      <a href="/login/?role=student" class="login-role-card">
        <div class="role-icon student"><i class="fas fa-user-graduate"></i></div>
        <h3>Student</h3>
        <span>Access your classes</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/login/?role=teacher" class="login-role-card">
        <div class="role-icon teacher"><i class="fas fa-chalkboard-teacher"></i></div>
        <h3>Teacher</h3>
        <span>Manage your courses</span>
      </a>
      <a href="/login/?role=admin" class="login-role-card">
        <div class="role-icon admin"><i class="fas fa-user-shield"></i></div>
        <h3>Admin</h3>
        <span>System management</span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<!-- ========== PAGE HEADER ========== -->
<section class="page-header">
  <div class="container">
    <h1>Founder &amp; Managing Trustee</h1>
    <div class="breadcrumb">
      <a href="/">Home</a> <i class="fas fa-chevron-right" style="font-size:.625rem"></i> <a href="/about/">About</a> <i class="fas fa-chevron-right" style="font-size:.625rem"></i> <span>Founder &amp; Trustees</span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== FOUNDER & TRUSTEES SECTION ========== -->
<section class="programs-section" data-aos="fade-up">
  <div class="container">

    <div class="section-header" style="text-align:center;margin-bottom:48px" data-aos="fade-up">
      <h2 style="font-size:2rem;font-weight:800;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:12px">Our Founder &amp; Trustees</h2>
      <p style="color:var(--gray-500);font-size:1.125rem;max-width:640px;margin:0 auto">The visionary leaders driving ENF's mission to empower underprivileged students across India.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="team-grid" style="display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:32px">

      <!-- 1. Er. Nagendra Singh -->
      <div class="team-card content-box" data-aos="fade-up" style="padding:32px">
        <div class="avatar-area" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <div class="avatar-circle" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,var(--primary),var(--accent));display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">NS</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:4px">Er. Nagendra Singh</h3>
            <span style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem">Managing Trustee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic">"A phenomenal growth of technical education in past decades have generated the need for the students to set high goals. Students getting guidance thrive well in the competition. As a Navodayan I feel my humble duty to dedicate all my efforts for betterment of great Nation by providing guidance to the students."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 2. Er. Brijesh Singh -->
      <div class="team-card content-box" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="100" style="padding:32px">
        <div class="avatar-area" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <div class="avatar-circle" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#065f46,#10b981);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">BS</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:4px">Er. Brijesh Singh</h3>
            <span style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem">Trustee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic">"I believe that success is not a one-day endeavour, but rather a result of persevering efforts. As Charles Darwin stated in the struggle for survival — the fittest win out at the expense of their rivals because they succeed in adapting themselves best to their environment."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 3. Er. Deepak Jaju -->
      <div class="team-card content-box" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="200" style="padding:32px">
        <div class="avatar-area" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <div class="avatar-circle" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#a78bfa);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">DJ</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:4px">Er. Deepak Jaju</h3>
            <span style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem">Trustee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic">"Competition is a race in which checking of thing occurs. A person requires confidence, sincerity, dedication, and a beautiful dream of AIM for winning the race. There are two kinds of people, one brilliant &amp; another hard-working, both can win the game."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 4. Dr. Arun Tiwari -->
      <div class="team-card content-box" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="300" style="padding:32px">
        <div class="avatar-area" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <div class="avatar-circle" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#b91c1c,#f87171);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">AT</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:4px">Dr. Arun Tiwari</h3>
            <span style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem">Trustee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic">"The medical field is part of the social field which is spreading on a large scale nowadays, and we are feeling proud of being part of that. As for Biology part, it's very interesting and creates the problem of leveling effect in scoring the marks in medical exams."</p>
      </div>

      <!-- 5. Mr. Dharmendra Singh -->
      <div class="team-card content-box" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-delay="400" style="padding:32px">
        <div class="avatar-area" style="display:flex;align-items:center;gap:16px;margin-bottom:20px">
          <div class="avatar-circle" style="width:64px;height:64px;border-radius:50%;background:linear-gradient(135deg,#0369a1,#38bdf8);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;color:#fff;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;flex-shrink:0">DS</div>
          <div>
            <h3 style="font-size:1.2rem;font-weight:700;color:var(--gray-900);margin-bottom:4px">Mr. Dharmendra Singh</h3>
            <span style="color:var(--primary);font-weight:600;font-size:.9rem">Trustee</span>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p style="color:var(--gray-500);line-height:1.8;font-style:italic">"When I think about education in every region of India, I get surprising results in success rates. Students which are awarded and got the opportunity for exposure in all the streams of career do well, at the same time, some potentially sounded students do not achieve their goals due to lack of guideline and awareness."</p>
      </div>

    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- ========== CTA SECTION ========== -->
<section class="cta-section" data-aos="fade-up">
  <div class="container">
    <h2>Join Us in Transforming Education</h2>
    <p style="color:rgba(255,255,255,.85);max-width:560px;margin:0 auto 24px">Support ENF's mission to empower underprivileged students with world-class education and resources.</p>
    <div class="cta-buttons">
      <a href="#contact" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Get Involved</a>
      <a href="/programs/" class="btn btn-outline-white btn-lg">Explore Programs</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

